        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=56575&amp;TOPIC_ID=6863&amp;FORUM_ID=2&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=General+Discussions&amp;Topic_Title=why+do+u+like+the+necro+class+so+much%3F&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         From a role playing stance:  I started out playing a ranger and have taken him to 52 (so far).  I loved being a champion of good and I worshipped Tunare like no other, devoting myself to her totally. While this was fun the truth of the matter is there is a side of me that wants to drag Tunare out in the forest, bend her over the nearest fallen tree and give that uptight bitch the business.  Hence my choice to turn to the dark side.</P><P>From a real life stance:  Most of my playing time is spent solo, part from necessity but mostly from desire.  The necro allows me to solo like no other class really can.  While I have always enjoyed EQ I am having fun now like never before since starting my necro. </P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
