        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=56699&amp;TOPIC_ID=6863&amp;FORUM_ID=2&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=General+Discussions&amp;Topic_Title=why+do+u+like+the+necro+class+so+much%3F&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I have made a level 60 vah shir rogue.  Was the first Vah Shir Assassin on my server.  I wanted to now make a seru bane weapon.  It takes meteor dust, shiknar ichor, fungoid sap, ssra blood, yttrium ore.  Well a rogue cannot solo for that stuff so I whip out the old necro.</P><P>I had tons of the the other stuff from camping lucid shards, working om Emperor key so only needed fugoid sap.  Fungoid sap drops off of Ancient Shriekers past the invisible bridge in the Deep.  On the way to the ancient shriekers there are piles of mobs, piles of see invis mobs and a lot of them cast.  My necro isn't exactly gimp to start with but I got an aego and divine strength and most importantly a sow.  On the Luclin server no one is ever in the zone unless doing THO or the Parasite.  I used the map from EQmaps.  I train all the way to the chasm knowing that shrooms don't see invis, so each time that a mob hits me I use my circlet of shadows to instantly invis.  Once to the chasm I cash harmshield and jump off the edge.  At the bottom I click off harmshield and feign death.  Wait two minutes, stand up, run up the far wall and start soloing mobs that hit for 250ish.  There isn't another class out there that could do the same as easily.  I also kill the 2 spawn of thought horrors just for fun when the shrooms are slow to spawn.  While your monk or SK might have a chance with the shrooms they'd be sorely underequiped for a thought horror evocer or spiriter.</P><P>I love my necro.</P><P></P><P>&lt;center&gt;<BR>&lt;a href=<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=177765&gt;Drainer" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=177765&gt;Drainer</a> the Heretic &lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;<BR>Warlock on Luclin &lt;br&gt;<BR>Legacy of Sorrow &lt;br&gt;<BR>Leader of Group 9 &lt;br&gt;<BR>&lt;/center&gt;<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
